com.vanillasource.gerec.mediatype

Class SameTypesMediaType<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vanillasource.gerec.mediatype.SameTypesMediaType<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AcceptMediaType<T>, ContentMediaType<T>, MediaType<T>

    public class SameTypesMediaType<T>
extends Object
implements MediaType<T>
    A collection of media-types that all produce the same java type. May be used in cases where the same object may have different representations, such as XML and JSON representations at the same time, or different versions of the same representation mapping to the same java class. The content type is the first media type given.
